te><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515925</guid></item><item><title>31 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃6</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515926</link><description>然后将我的钱转移到卡上，真是太浪漫了！</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515926</guid></item><item><title>31 Martha 2025的轶事＃7</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515927</link><description>鱿鱼游戏中最好的版本是鱿鱼游戏和啤酒。即使没有鱿鱼，您也可以玩。</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515927</guid></item><item><title>31 Martha 2025的轶事＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515928</link><description>我喜欢导航器中的那个女孩定期告诉我坚持下去。右边说，请坚持。&lt;br /&gt;亲爱的，我坚持下去。谢谢。</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515928</guid></item><item><title>31 Martha 2025的anecdot＃10</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515930</link><description>现代奴隶不在链条中，而是债务。</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515930</guid></item><item><title>31 Martha 2025的anecdot＃11</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515931</link><description>来自新闻：“在美国，一名妇女穿透了一个奇怪的房子，喂狗，然后洗了菜，然后离开。”&lt;br /&gt;评论：她明天有空吗？</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-31/#1515931</guid></item></channel></rss>